pol._1_paragraph:
Definitions
  	– Platform: the email info@Tokized.com  and all subordinate pages;
  	– Visitor: person who visits the Platform;
  	– Customer: person who places an order on the Platform.

pol._3_paragraph:
Personal data
  	Personal data that you provide us with:

  	IP address;
  	surfing behaviour;
  	origin;
  	search terms;
  	login data;
  	e-mail address;
  	profile picture;
  	contact details.
  	Tokized may collect data from you in several ways:

  	through the use of cookies;
  	during your registration or use of the platform;
  	by requesting further information, following contacts you have made with Tokized through this site;
  	when filling out forms for discussing your problem or contact names;
  	when entering, sharing and forwarding data at your initiative that you share with other users on our sites.

pol._4_paragraph:
Purposes of the processing
  	Tokized will only use the Personal Data collected from you for the following purposes:

  	managing your account on the Platform with a view to providing you with the best service possible, with the legal basis 
  	being the execution of an agreement requested by you;
  	sending you direct marketing, newsletters, promotions and promotions, with your explicit prior consent as legal basis;
  	adequately answering your questions regarding the Platform or for the provision of services, with the legal basis of 
  	providing a service that you have requested;
  	the verification of the uniqueness of the entered data and the veracity of the case.
  	You are not obliged to disclose your Personal Data, but understand that the provision of certain services becomes 
  	impossible if you refuse the processing.
